Taipei 5.0 Release Notes
------------------------

Hello!  I hope you enjoy playing Taipei 5.0.  Here's a partial list of
new features you'll enjoy:

	* Spiffy new Taipei background (yes, it's really Taipei!)
	* User defined tile layouts
	* Expanded help file
	* Watch tile layouts being built as an option
	* Many new fortunes
	* Options saved in WIN.INI file
